body: Hi I wanna create a zone but has a problem about Open studio standard file. I did download from link([https://app.box.com/s/bh9sbpgajdtmmystv3n4](https://app.box.com/s/bh9sbpgajdtmmystv3n4)) and copy to Ladybug path but yet has the same problem How can I solve this problem? thanks inadvance MSM [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/KzOvBNTGFEHdcKTEVDT9NlqjdbX4KlP6e1TtGEBfBSvLN1evBcYFYZOizSsQTexS7tJBkn1IHoHF1JQrvsVsVMq*w-ymFmM3/12.jpg)

replies.body:
Hi Masoome.

1. Make sure to copy it to the right folder. It can be c:\ladybug or C:\Users\%USERNAME%\AppData\Roaming\Ladybug as Peter has already sent you the link.

2. Right click and Grasshopper canvas and try to re-compute.

Mostapha
Thanks a lot. I was wrong about the path
